{"tid":853060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[金球獎]  30人提名名單陸續公佈 艾利臣比加首次入圍","createTime":"2018-10-08T10:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T05:02:03.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e79fe2514e5fcdda45bcb1d095ff29d833df0ea3","tid":853060,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:02:43.000Z","msg":"2018年度最後的球壇頒獎禮金球獎，將於12月3日在巴黎舉行，主辦單位法國足球雜誌，今日陸續公佈最後的30人提名名單，首5人分別是加里夫巴利（皇家馬德里/威爾斯）、阿古路（曼城/阿根廷）、艾利臣比加（利物浦/巴西）、賓施馬（皇家馬德里/法國）、卡雲尼（巴黎聖日耳門/烏拉圭）。<br />\n<br />\n上屆金球獎由基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）大熱勝出，今屆大熱門是皇家馬德里中場兼克羅地亞隊長莫迪歷，這位33歲中場今年已勇奪世界足球先生及上季歐洲最佳球員等大獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賓施馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef9333bd220d67d915f56d874e55f8a952c8c80","tid":853060,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:07:16.000Z","msg":"阿古路（曼城/阿根廷）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c846ec439a757603eb0a5e8537354c3855fcaa6","tid":853060,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"足球先生同金球獎投票方式係咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果一樣都係由堆隊長教練投其實結果都唔會點變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb37cefd9af6e420728fd8d0ada2b632be72270b","tid":853060,"uid":581,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/08/180842_f6bc3127756a8921119473c546d7c84b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F08%2F180842_f6bc3127756a8921119473c546d7c84b.png&h=fa9aa5ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9789e6ed88187258694295438a5ff67e53f02143","tid":853060,"uid":581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-